track_notes: I activated late afternoon so there was no one playing golf. Permission therefore was not sought. Week Lane is a little rough but OK for an SUV. Plenty room for one to park half way down it. Took me 23 mins to walk to the activation point near one of the tees close to the trig point.
track_title: Park part way down Week Lane or at end of it

track_notes: Total time (including ops): 1h 5m. Maximum difficulty: Swiss Alpine Club Grade T1. Uncurated GPX which may contain navigation errors, detours and hazards.
